snippet: Canada stormed into the semifinals of the world championship for the first time in six years with a 9-0 rout of Belarus in Prague.
abstract: Canada men's hockey team routs Belarus, 9-0, to reach world championship semifinals; other matches noted.
lead_paragraph: Canada stormed into the semifinals of the world championship for the first time in six years with a 9-0 rout of Belarus in Prague.
